Program: Outlook
Title: $65m for gay daughter's hand
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p010d969
Last Broadcast Date: Tue 20 Nov 2012
Jo Fidgen talks to Gigi Chao, the Chinese gay socialite whose father offered $65 million dollars to any man who could convince her to marry him. Also, the glamorous MTV presenter from Germany explains why she risked losing her career and her family to convert to Islam. Image: Cecil (l) and Gigi Chao (r) Show less